    User ericg
    ForwardX11 yes
    ForwardX11Trusted yes
    ForwardAgent yes

Host *.elfwerks.org
    User ericg
    ForwardX11 yes
    ForwardAgent yes

Host *.elfwerks.net
    User gustafer
    ForwardX11 yes
    ForwardAgent yes
    UserKnownHostsFile /dev/null
    StrictHostKeyChecking no

